# Egress allow-list — regex matched against the request's hostname.
# Each line is a Python-flavored regex. Anchored with ^...$ to avoid
# accidental matches on subdomain segments (`evil-github.com` etc.).
#
# To add a new destination, list it here AND have it reviewed in a PR —
# this file is the L0 network egress policy.
^github\.com$
^.+\.github\.com$
^.+\.githubusercontent\.com$
^api\.anthropic\.com$
# PyPI mirrors (used by ruff/pytest cache misses; safe defaults)
^pypi\.org$
^files\.pythonhosted\.org$
